---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Jerry Chen — computer science at McGill, working across SWE, AI, and NLP research."
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl">About</h1>

  <section class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:gap-8">
    <figure
      class="shrink-0 overflow-hidden border border-border bg-surface"
      style="width: 180px; aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/jerry.jpg"
        alt="Jerry Chen"
        width="180"
        height="225"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      />
    </figure>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        I'm Jerry Chen — an undergraduate B.Sc. Honours Computer Science
        student (minor in Statistics) at McGill University. I'm currently
        figuring out where I want to put my time, somewhere between SWE and AI
        internships, startup ideas, and NLP research.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of that, I'm into fashion and sustainability, and play with the
        Inter Montreal soccer team. Ultimately I'm trying to find the
        intersection between my skills and the things I actually care about.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
      What I work on
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
      <p>
        My work spans three loose tracks. <strong>Software engineering</strong>{" "}
        — typical full-stack and systems projects, the kind of work you do to
        ship things that people actually use.{" "}
        <strong>AI development</strong> — building with LLMs and foundation
        models, applied rather than theoretical.{" "}
        <strong>NLP / LLM research</strong> — a more academic slice, closer to
        understanding how these models work than shipping features with them.
      </p>
      <p>
        Projects on this site are tagged
        <a href="/projects?tag=swe">SWE</a>,
        <a href="/projects?tag=ai">AI</a>, or
        <a href="/projects?tag=nlp">NLP</a> so you can filter to the track you
        care about.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
      Elsewhere
    </h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 flex gap-5">
      <li>
        <a
          href="mailto:ch.jerry23@gmail.com"
          aria-label="Email Jerry"
          class="icon-link"
        >
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            width="22"
            height="22"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"></rect>
            <path d="m3 7 9 6 9-6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Lil-Chen05"
          aria-label="GitHub profile"
          class="icon-link"
        >
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            width="22"
            height="22"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M12 .3a12 12 0 0 0-3.8 23.4c.6.1.8-.3.8-.6v-2c-3.3.7-4-1.6-4-1.6-.6-1.4-1.4-1.8-1.4-1.8-1-.7.1-.7.1-.7 1.2.1 1.9 1.2 1.9 1.2 1 1.8 2.8 1.3 3.5 1 .1-.8.4-1.3.8-1.6-2.7-.3-5.5-1.3-5.5-6 0-1.2.5-2.3 1.3-3.1-.2-.4-.6-1.6 0-3.2 0 0 1-.3 3.4 1.2a11.5 11.5 0 0 1 6 0c2.3-1.5 3.3-1.2 3.3-1.2.7 1.6.2 2.9.1 3.2.8.8 1.3 1.9 1.3 3.2 0 4.6-2.8 5.6-5.5 5.9.5.4.9 1.2.9 2.3v3.3c0 .3.1.7.8.6A12 12 0 0 0 12 .3Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jerry-chen-63a248289/"
          aria-label="LinkedIn profile"
          class="icon-link"
        >
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            width="22"
            height="22"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M20.5 2h-17A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2 3.5v17A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3.5 22h17a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-17A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 20.5 2zM8 19H5V9h3v10zM6.5 7.7A1.75 1.75 0 1 1 6.5 4.2a1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 3.5zM19 19h-3v-5.3c0-1.3-.5-2.2-1.7-2.2a1.9 1.9 0 0 0-1.7 1.2 2.4 2.4 0 0 0-.1.8V19h-3V9h3v1.3a3 3 0 0 1 2.7-1.5c2 0 3.4 1.3 3.4 4.1V19z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <style>
      .icon-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.12s ease;
      }
      .icon-link:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
      }
    </style>
  </section>
</Layout>
